    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You make a calming gesture, and up to three willing creatures of your choice that you can see within range fall unconscious for the power\u2019s duration. The power ends on a target early if it takes damage or someone uses an action to shake or slap it awake. If a target remains unconscious for the full duration, that target gains the benefit of a short rest, and it can\u2019t be affected by this power again until it finishes a long rest.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Force Potency.</strong></em>&nbsp;When you cast this power using a force slot of 4th level or higher, you can target one additional willing creature for each slot level above 3rd.</p>",
